n	\n		\n\n	\n	\n	\n\n		English Conversation Circle – Bloor/Gladstone Library\n	\n\n\n					\n	\n		Bloor/Gladstone Library	\n	\n		1101 Bloor Street West\, Toronto\, Ontario\, Canada	\n	\n									\n\n				\n	Are you new to Canada as a Permanent Resident or a Convention Refugee? Practice English in small groups\, with the support of our Mentors! 8 weekly sessions Speak with confidence […] \n\n				\n			\n		\n	\n\n\n\n							\n				\n				\n\n	\n	\n		\n			Tue		\n		\n			10		\n	\n\n\n	\n		\n			\n	\n\n\n			\n\n				\n					\n	\n		English Conversation Circle – Daniel G. Hill	\n\n					\n		\n		March 10 @ 11:00 am - 12:30 pm	\n	\n\n	\n		\n\n	\n	\n	\n\n		English Conversation Circle – Daniel G. Hill\n	\n\n\n					\n	\n		Daniel G. Hill Library	\n	\n		620 Jane Street\, Toronto\, Ontario\, Canada	\n	\n									\n\n				\n	Are you new to Canada as a Permanent Resident or a Convention Refugee? Practice English in small groups\, with the support of our Mentors! 8 weekly sessions Speak with confidence […] \n\n				\n			\n		\n	\n\n\n\n							\n				\n				\n\n	\n	\n		\n			Tue		\n		\n			10		\n	\n\n\n	\n		\n			\n	\n\n\n			\n\n				\n					\n	\n		Musuem Tour & Art Activity	\n\n					\n		\n		March 10 @ 1:00 pm - 4:30 pm	\n	\n														\n\n				\n	Join us for a tour of the Royal Ontario Museum! Free tour of the Royal Ontario Museum\, including the featured exhibition: Wildlife Photographer of the Year 2025 Create your own […] \n\n				\n			\n		\n	\n\n\n\n							\n				\n				\n\n	\n	\n		\n			Tue		\n		\n			10		\n	\n\n\n	\n		\n			\n	\n\n\n			\n\n				\n					\n	\n		Looking For Volunteers: Content Creator Crew!	\n\n					\n		\n		March 10 @ 2:00 pm - 4:00 pm	\n	\n\n	\n		\n\n	\n	\n	\n\n		Looking For Volunteers: Content Creator Crew!\n	\n\n\n					\n	\n		Parkdale Library	\n	\n		1303 Queen Street West\, Toronto\, Ontario\, Canada	\n	\n									\n\n				\n	Love TikTok + Instagram? Turn your creativity into real experience What you'll do: Take photos + short videos Capture behind-the-scenes moments Help edit Reels/TikToks (simple + guided) Support social media […] \n\n				\n			\n		\n	\n\n\n\n							\n				\n				\n\n	\n	\n		\n			Tue		\n		\n			10		\n	\n\n\n	\n		\n			\n	\n\n\n			\n\n				\n					\n	\n		English Conversation Circle – Forest Hill Library	\n\n					\n		\n		March 10 @ 6:00 pm - 7:30 pm	\n	\n\n	\n		\n\n	\n	\n	\n\n		English Conversation Circle – Forest Hill Library\n	\n\n\n														\n\n				\n	Are you new to Canada as a Permanent Resident or a Convention Refugee? Practice English in small groups\, with the support of our Mentors! 8 weekly sessions Speak with confidence […] \n\n				\n			\n		\n	\n\n\n\n							\n				\n				\n\n	\n	\n		\n			Tue		\n		\n			10		\n	\n\n\n	\n		\n			\n	\n\n\n			\n\n				\n					\n	\n		Citizenship Education Circle – Toronto Reference Library	\n\n					\n		\n		March 10 @ 6:00 pm - 8:30 pm	\n	\n\n	\n		\n\n	\n	\n	\n\n		Citizenship Education Circle – Toronto Reference Library\n	\n\n\n					\n	\n		Toronto Reference Library	\n	\n		789 Yonge Street\, Toronto\, Ontario\, Canada	\n	\n									\n\n				\n	Are you new to Canada as a Permanent Resident or a Convention Refugee? Every Tuesday at the Toronto Reference Library there will be free weekly sessions to prepare for the […] \n\n				\n			\n		\n	\n\n\n\n							\n				\n				\n\n	\n	\n		\n			Wed		\n		\n			11		\n	\n\n\n	\n		\n			\n	\n\n\n			\n\n				\n					\n	\n		Seniors 55+ Zoo to You!	\n\n					\n		\n		March 11 @ 1:00 pm - 3:30 pm	\n	\n					\n	\n		Lilian H Smith Library	\n	\n		239 College Street\, Toronto\, Ontario\, Canada	\n	\n									\n\n				\n	Learn about various animals! For more information or to register\, contact Farifta at frahman@culturelink.ca or call at 437-488-8960 \n\n				\n			\n		\n	\n\n\n\n							\n				\n				\n\n	\n	\n		\n			Wed		\n		\n			11		\n	\n\n\n	\n		\n			\n	\n\n\n			\n\n				\n					\n	\n		Create Learn Connect	\n\n					\n		\n		March 11 @ 2:00 pm - 4:00 pm	\n	\n\n	\n		\n\n	\n	\n	\n\n		Create Learn Connect\n	\n\n\n					\n	\n		Cecil Street Community Centre	\n	\n		58 Cecil Street\, Toronto\, Ontario\, Canada	\n	\n									\n\n				\n	Nurture Your Artistic Potential! Our thoughtfully designed Art Workshops encourage creativity\, focus\, and growth Participants must be a Permanent Resident or Convention Refugee and at least 19 years old. To […] \n\n				\n			\n		\n	\n\n\n\n							\n				\n				\n\n	\n	\n		\n			Thu		\n		\n			12		\n	\n\n\n	\n		\n			\n	\n\n\n			\n\n				\n					\n	\n		G1 Driving Test Classes for Newcomers	\n\n					\n		\n		March 12 @ 2:00 pm - 4:00 pm	\n	\n\n	\n		\n\n	\n	\n	\n\n		G1 Driving Test Classes for Newcomers\n	\n\n\n					\n	\n		CultureLink	\n	\n		2340 Dundas St W\, Toronto\, Ontario\, Canada	\n	\n									\n\n				\n	Get ready to pass your Ontario G1 Knowledge Test for Free! Program Highlights: Instructor-led\, easy-to-follow lessons MTO-approved materials Supportive and welcoming learning environment Ideal for first-time drivers and newcomers Who […] \n\n				\n			\n		\n	\n\n\n\n							\n				\n				\n\n	\n	\n		\n			Thu		\n		\n			12		\n	\n\n\n	\n		\n			\n	\n\n\n			\n\n				\n					\n	\n		Content Creation for Success	\n\n					\n		\n		March 12 @ 4:00 pm - 5:00 pm	\n	\n\n	\n		\n\n	\n	\n	\n\n		Content Creation for Success\n	\n\n\n					\n	\n		CultureLink Children & Youth Centre	\n	\n		3535 Dundas Street West\, Toronto\, Ontario\, Canada	\n	\n									\n\n				\n	Free Workshops For Youth\, Ages 16-30 Learn directly from real influencers! Live Q&A - ask creators anything (growth\, money\, fame) Secrets behind viral videos + follower growth Film + edit […] \n\n				\n			\n		\n	\n\n\n\n							\n				\n				\n\n	\n	\n		\n			Thu		\n		\n			12		\n	\n\n\n	\n		\n			\n	\n\n\n			\n\n				\n					\n	\n		English Conversation Circle – New Toronto Library	\n\n					\n		\n		March 12 @ 6:00 pm	\n	\n\n	\n		\n\n	\n	\n	\n\n		English Conversation Circle – New Toronto Library\n	\n\n\n					\n	\n		New Toronto Library	\n	\n		110 Eleventh Street\, Toronto\, Ontario\, Canada	\n	\n									\n\n				\n	Are you new to Canada as a Permanent Resident or a Convention Refugee? Practice English in small groups\, with the support of our Mentors! 8 weekly sessions Speak with confidence […] \n\n				\n			\n		\n	\n\n\n\n			\n		\n\n		\n	\n		\n	\n		\n	\n\n		\n			Previous Events		\n	\n\n\n		\n	\n		Today	\n\n\n		\n	\n		\n			Next Events		\n		\n	\n\n	\n\n	\n\n\n		\n	\n		\n			\n				Subscribe to calendar			\n			\n	\n\n		\n		\n			\n									\n\n	\n		Google Calendar	\n\n									\n\n	\n		iCalendar	\n\n									\n\n	\n		Outlook 365	\n\n									\n\n	\n		Outlook Live	\n\n									\n\n	\n		Export .ics file	\n\n									\n\n	\n		Export Outlook .ics file
